<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> die
                            <expan>hernachges<ex>chriben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wie in der edell
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der von Eppenstein, in
                                <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> geleite
                            <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hab <expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ut <expan>su<ex>pra</ex></expan>
<expan>p<ex>rae</ex>cise</expan>
<add><expan>usq<ex>ue</ex></expan></add>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnedige <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne
                                <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz in dieselb ir hab wider
                        und on hindernüsse volg und werde, als etc. Das
                            <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
